          <p class="ba-sub">For local businesses wanting GBP optimization, local rank tracking, and citation management at the lowest possible price.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Localo is the most affordable dedicated local SEO tool. It provides GBP post templates, a local rank tracking grid, and citation management for $19–69/month. For a local business that wants to improve its GBP presence and monitor local rankings without spending $39–59/month on BrightLocal's full suite, Localo provides a useful entry point. The GBP post templates help structure your monthly posts — but you still write the content. For automated GBP content, theStacc's Local SEO module at $49/month is the better investment: it writes and publishes 30 GBP posts per month without your involvement.</p>
