        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Local Falcon specializes in one thing: showing exactly where you rank in Google Maps across a geographic grid. At $24.99/month (credit-based), it's the most detailed local rank visualization tool under $100. You choose the grid size (3x3 to 13x13 points) and scan radius. Each scan shows your ranking at every grid point and lets you benchmark against competitors. For a dentist or plumber wanting to understand exactly which neighborhoods they're invisible in, Local Falcon provides the most actionable data available at this price point.</p>
